naissance's most illustrious women writers"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 43 0aEnglish literatureyEarly modern, 1500-1700xHistory and criticism. 0aEnglish literaturexWomen authorsxHistory and criticism. 0aGrief in literature. 0aRenaissancezEngland.423Cover imageuhttp://assets.cambridge.org/97811070/79984/cover/9781107079984.jpg  aPR 113 H59 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035231651  aPR 113 H59 2015wLCc1i0162034577633d2/12/2015e2/9/2015lON_SHELFmUAAUGn1p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/4/2015  aPR 113 H59 2015wLCc1i0162035243680lON_SHELFmUAHSSp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/26/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2014060900bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/70708929